flowchart TD
  Upload[XLSX upload / GCS URI] --> Ingest[POST /ingest sync]
  Ingest --> Guardrails[SSRF guard / MAX_INGEST_BYTES / dedup lock]
  Guardrails --> Raw[GCS raw artifact audit]
  Guardrails --> Normalize[Readers + cleanup + canonical model]
  Normalize --> Identity[Identity resolution]
  Identity --> Features[RFM / BTYD / CLV / customer_features]
  Features --> Freshness[Freshness]
  Features --> LedgerOutbox[measurement_outbox]
  LedgerOutbox --> Exporter[Exporter Cloud Run Job]
  Exporter --> BigQuery[(BigQuery measurement)]
  Features --> DataQuality[Data quality detector]
  DataQuality --> Triage[LLM triage + review queue]
  Triage --> WAP[Write-Audit-Publish circuit breaker]
  WAP --> BigQuery

